    "media_id": "17900000000000000",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000000",
    "text": "The North Sea looks almost Baltic-calm here. Was this taken first thing this morning?",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-10T16:55:59+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000002",
    "username": "erik_nordsee"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000001",
    "like_count": "17",
    "media_id": "17900000000000001",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000001",
    "text": "That hull section looks Hanseatic, 15th c. probably. Any chance of a higher-res image of the planking?",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-09T14:08:41+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000003",
    "username": "astrid_archaeo"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000002",
    "like_count": "6",
    "media_id": "17900000000000002",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000002",
    "text": "Beautiful in-situ recording. That's the kind of patience the discipline runs on. Which survey area is this?",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-10T00:19:34+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000004",
    "username": "lars_kuestenerbe"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000003",
    "like_count": "9",
    "media_id": "17900000000000003",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000003",
    "text": "Will the open day include the conservation lab tour again? Bringing the whole family this year.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-10T20:11:11+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000005",
    "username": "sigrid_sylt"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000004",
    "like_count": "1",
    "media_id": "17900000000000000",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000000",
    "text": "That's the North Frisian survey grid at low tide. Anja spotted the first wreck timbers herself - she's got the eye. - bjørn",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-09T01:34:22+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000006",
    "username": "bjørn_diver"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000005",
    "like_count": "24",
    "media_id": "17900000000000001",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000001",
    "text": "Is this the Sylt wreck? The preservation on that bow section is remarkable. Looking forward to the dendro results.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-09T20:14:29+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000007",
    "username": "dr_moe_curator"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000006",
    "like_count": "13",
    "media_id": "17900000000000000",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000000",
    "text": "Beautiful light on the water here.",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-03T16:55:59+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000002",
    "username": "erik_nordsee"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000007",
    "like_count": "17",
    "media_id": "17900000000000001",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000001",
    "text": "Is this from the autumn survey window?",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-01T14:08:41+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000003",
    "username": "astrid_archaeo"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000008",
    "like_count": "6",
    "media_id": "17900000000000002",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000002",
    "text": "The wreck timbers look remarkably preserved.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-22T00:19:34+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000004",
    "username": "lars_kuestenerbe"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000009",
    "like_count": "9",
    "media_id": "17900000000000003",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000003",
    "text": "Thank you for sharing the public lecture details.",
    "timestamp": "2025-10-19T20:11:11+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000005",
    "username": "sigrid_sylt"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000010",
    "like_count": "1",
    "media_id": "17900000000000000",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000000",
    "text": "Will there be a recording of the talk?",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-09T01:34:22+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000006",
    "username": "bjørn_diver"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000011",
    "like_count": "24",
    "media_id": "17900000000000001",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000001",
    "text": "Fascinating - love the sonar overlay.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-01T20:14:29+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000007",
    "username": "dr_moe_curator"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000012",
    "like_count": "13",
    "media_id": "17900000000000000",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000000",
    "text": "Congratulations to the whole survey team.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-21T16:55:59+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000002",
    "username": "erik_nordsee"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000013",
    "like_count": "17",
    "media_id": "17900000000000001",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000001",
    "text": "The conservation work is so important.",
    "timestamp": "2026-01-25T14:08:41+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000003",
    "username": "astrid_archaeo"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000014",
    "like_count": "6",
    "media_id": "17900000000000002",
    "parent_id": "17900000000000002",
    "text": "Looking forward to the museum exhibition.",
